00:32:25,450 --> 00:32:26,550
I'm not.

557
00:32:32,470 --> 00:32:34,060
Lea makes me happy.

558
00:32:38,760 --> 00:32:41,410
Well, Lea's not the only one that can do that.

559
00:32:45,930 --> 00:32:47,140
I'm gonna miss you.

560
00:32:51,230 --> 00:32:52,560
Your BNP.

561
00:32:54,850 --> 00:32:57,050
Jenny Kunkler's - cardio protein levels are...

562
00:32:57,050 --> 00:32:58,950
I've never seen anything like it.

563
00:32:58,950 --> 00:33:03,540
That's because the levels are for two hearts, not one.

564
00:33:03,540 --> 00:33:05,570
Now Jenny is killing Katie!

